longBusinessSummary: Longhui International Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the hotpot restaurant business in the People's Republic of China. It owns and operates restaurants under the Faigo and Xiao Faigo Hotpot brands. The company is based in Central, Hong Kong.
